{
  "texts": [
    "In summary, we observed that GPT-4o with CoT-SC and CoT obtained the best performance across all the proficiency levels.",
    "GPT-4o with CoT-SC resulted in 0.6 errors (on average) for the 149 easy questions, 22.4 errors for the 392 difficult questions, and 24.4 errors for the 157 expert-level questions.",
    "CoT obtained the least errors (i.e., 9.6) for the 352 moderate-level questions.",
    "GPT-4o was also the most accurate model across all domains.",
    "GPT-4o with CoT-SC recorded only 7 errors in the D1) principles of dietetics questions and 18.2 errors in the D4) food and nutrition management questions."
  ]
}